_sText:
5th version of the original.. and still innovating!  Fixed many other glitches that u guyz keep on discovering, and i thank you all!

Fixed:
-pipes, they're not random anymore, they act like the last trap
-3 pillars, cant pass anymore on wall side
-bird, ok, wont flap its wings anymore, so wont act stupidly such as doing backflips and stuff like! lol
-fence, you were right, just didnt fit in.. so i changed the model for something already in the map
-elevator, changed the way it looked.
-late spawners will be punished!

Added:
-HDR effect
-new skybox (again)

i don't expect to do a 6th version but i told so on babylon_final! keep on leaving your comments, that helps me improving my skills and pushes the original babylon version far in our .. mind!

-Hoops aka duff
